Starting Armor (Choose one appropriate, likely from "Vampire Class", "Forbidden Scholar / Cultist Class", or Universal lists):
Nightshade Cloak (Vampire Class) ‚Äì Reduces Damage by 1, grants Stealth bonus. Shadow damage resistance
Woven Shadows (Forbidden Scholar / Cultist Class) ‚Äì Reduces Damage by 2, +1 to DR when resisting mind-affecting effects
Traveler‚Äôs Leathers (Universal) ‚Äì +1 DV, no penalties to movement or Stealth
Sangromancer (Blood Mage Archetype)
Starting Weapon (Choose one from "Blood Mage Class" list):
Bloodstaff ‚Äì Damage: 3 ‚Äì Heals caster instead of damage (This is the example given in character creation )
Veinbinder Rod ‚Äì Damage: 4 ‚Äì Targets take 1 damage per round unless healed
Crimson Spear ‚Äì Damage: 5 ‚Äì Range 2 tiles; caster gains 1 HP on crit
Starting Armor (Choose one appropriate from "Blood Mage Class" list):
Veinsilk Robes ‚Äì Reduces Damage by 1, caster heals 1 HP after casting a Blood spell (This is the example given in character creation )
Sanguine Mantle ‚Äì Reduces Damage by 2, add +1 to Blood spell damage once per round
Arterywraps ‚Äì Reduces Damage by 1, cast 1 Tier 1 Blood spell as a reaction once per scene
Glyph Seeker
Starting Weapon (Choose one, likely Universal or a simple weapon if no direct list applies):
Spiritshard Wand (Universal) ‚Äì Damage: 3 (Spiritual) ‚Äì Ranged spiritual weapon; pass through walls within spectral realm (Requires Soul > 2)
Throwing Dagger (Universal) ‚Äì Damage: 3 ‚Äì Thrown (Range 8 tiles); mark target for 1 turn (If not focused on direct combat)
Starting Armor (Choose one appropriate, likely from "Forbidden Scholar / Cultist Class" or Universal lists):
Ritual Vestments (Forbidden Scholar / Cultist Class) ‚Äì Reduces Damage by 1, reduce corruption cost by 1 (min 1) for one spell per scene
