Weapons and Armor List
This document lists both class-specific and universal weapons available in the Legacy of Kain: Bloodbound RPG. All weapons deal a fixed amount of damage on a successful hit. Traits indicate special effects triggered on hits or conditions.

üßô Class-Specific Weapons
Vampire Class
Scion Blade ‚Äì Damage: 6 ‚Äì Bleed on crit; +1 damage if gained a blood point this round.
Bloodfang Dagger ‚Äì Damage: 4 ‚Äì +2 damage when targeting a bleeding foe.
Nightblade Saber ‚Äì Damage: 5 ‚Äì +1 armor penetration; silent and swift.
Sarafan Crusader Class
Sarafan Pike ‚Äì Damage: 5 ‚Äì Reach 2 tiles; +2 damage vs. Undead.
Blessed Mace ‚Äì Damage: 6 ‚Äì On hit, undead must succeed DR 2 or be stunned.
Crusader Broadsword ‚Äì Damage: 5 ‚Äì +1 DV when wielded; balanced and blessed.
Wraith / Spirit-Bound Class
Spectral Talons ‚Äì Damage: 4 (Spiritual) ‚Äì Ignores armor; requires Spectral Realm.
Echoblade ‚Äì Damage: 5 ‚Äì On hit, copy last minor spell cast.
Phantom Claws ‚Äì Damage: 3 ‚Äì On hit, inflict -1 on enemy rolls for 1 round.
Blood Mage Class
Bloodstaff ‚Äì Damage: 3 ‚Äì Heals caster instead of damage.
Veinbinder Rod ‚Äì Damage: 4 ‚Äì Targets take 1 damage per round unless healed.
Crimson Spear ‚Äì Damage: 5 ‚Äì Range 2 tiles; caster gains 1 HP on crit.
Forbidden Scholar / Cultist Class
Hexbrand ‚Äì Damage: 5 ‚Äì Target gains 1 Corruption; disrupts next spell.
Ritual Blade ‚Äì Damage: 4 ‚Äì On crit, absorb 1 Soul Energy.
Whisperknife ‚Äì Damage: 3 ‚Äì Can be summoned and dismissed freely; bypasses normal wards.

